  For every event: state the motive/cause FIRST, then the action/result.

MICRO-CALLBACK (max 1-4 sentences):
  If you need to reference a past event to explain the present, keep it to 1-4 sentences.
  Do NOT write full flashback paragraphs.
  ✓ "Blackbeard đã mất 30 thủy thủ vì bệnh scurvy 3 tháng trước.
