HEART phases (Giao Tranh, Quyết Định):
  - Visceral, fast, staccato
  - Short sentences for impact, fragments for drama
  - Focus on WHAT IT WAS LIKE — chaos, sensory overload, fog of war
  - POV: third-person with second-person soldier moments (Adrenaline Test)
  - Techniques: Visceral Sensory Detail, Escalation, Foreshadowing

HOOK (Mở Màn):
