HOOK CHAPTER RULES
═══════════════════════════════════════

If this is the hook chapter, follow the framework's `hook` rules:

The hook has 3 CORE ELEMENTS (same as Deep-Dive):

  1. SHOCKING OUTCOME — Show the END FIRST.
